# Template Formatting Fix Walkthrough

This walkthrough documents the successful activation of a custom template loader to handle broken Django template tags caused by auto-formatters.

## Problem
Auto-formatters (like Prettier) were splitting Django template tags across multiple lines, causing rendering errors or visible raw code in the browser.
Example of broken syntax:
```django
{%
  some_tag
%}
```

## Solution
We enabled the `FixedTemplateLoader` in `d:\net2000\core\settings.py`. This custom loader detects these split tags and rejoins them before Django's parser processes them.

### Changes
1.  **Modified [core/settings.py](file:///d:/net2000/core/settings.py)**:
    -   Configured `TEMPLATES` to use explicit `loaders`.
    -   Added `manager.template_loaders.FixedTemplateLoader` as the primary loader.
    -   Manually added `d:\net2000\manager\templates` to `DIRS` to ensure the custom loader processes the app's templates.

```python
# settings.py snippet
'loaders': [
    'manager.template_loaders.FixedTemplateLoader',
    'django.template.loaders.filesystem.Loader',
    'django.template.loaders.app_directories.Loader',
],
```

## Verification
-   **Server Health**: The Django development server reloaded successfully without errors.
-   **Page Rendering**: Validated that `http://127.0.0.1:8000/history/` returns a successful response (Status 200) and content renders correctly, indicating the templates are being processed by the fix.

# Full-Screen History Table Walkthrough

This walkthrough details the changes made to make the Transaction History table fill the entire page width and height, utilizing a modern, responsive layout.

## Changes

### 1. Flexible Container in `base.html`
We modified the base template to allow child pages to override the main container class.
```html
<!-- base.html -->
<div class="{% block container_class %}container{% endblock %} flex-grow-1">
```

### 2. Full-Screen Layout in `history.html`
We completely restructured the history page to use:
-   **`container-fluid`**: To span the full width of the viewport.
-   **Flexbox Columns**: To organize the header, stats, and table vertically.
-   **`flex-grow-1`**: To force the table container to expand and fill all remaining vertical space.
-   **Sticky Header**: Added `sticky-top` to the table header so it remains visible while scrolling the table body.

```html
<!-- history.html structure -->
{% block container_class %}container-fluid d-flex flex-column{% endblock %}

<div class="d-flex flex-column h-100">
    <!-- Header & Stats (Fixed Height) -->
    <div class="pt-3 px-3">...</div>

    <!-- Table Container (Fills Remaining Space) -->
    <div class="card ... flex-grow-1 mx-3 mb-3">
        <div class="table-responsive h-100 overflow-auto">
            <table class="table ...">
                <thead class="sticky-top">...</thead>
                ...
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
```

## Verification
-   **Full Width**: The table now extends to the edges of the window (with small margins).
-   **Full Height**: The table container pushes to the bottom of the page (above the footer).
-   **Scrolling**: If the table content exceeds the viewable area, a vertical scrollbar appears *within the table card*, keeping the header and page stats visible.

# Printed Receipt A4 Optimization

This section details the CSS adjustments made to ensure the daily receipt prints effectively on A4 paper.

## Changes
Modified `manager/receipt.html` inside the `@media print` block:
-   **Margins & Orientation**: Set standard `1cm` margins and `landscape` orientation.
-   **Font Sizes**: Increased body text to `11pt` (from 7pt), headers to `16pt`/`12pt`, and table text to `10pt` for better readability and to fill the page.
-   **Table Layout**:
    -   Removed fixed narrow widths    -   **Category Tabs**: Replaced the search bar idea with **Category Tabs** in the modal header.
        -   Users can click "All" or specific categories (e.g., "Hot Options") to filter the list instantly.
        -   Verified that filtering is robust and adding items from filtered views functions correctly.
    -   **Verification**: Visually confirmed the wider modal layout, static text, and tab functionality using browser simulation.
-   **Bug Fixes**:
    -   **Copy/Fax 500 Error**: Fixed a variable shadowing issue in [add_copy](file:///d:/net2000/manager/views.py#616-659) and [add_fax](file:///d:/net2000/manager/views.py#579-614) views that caused a server error upon confirmation. Verified both features now work correctly.

